description:
Included are arguably the greatest songs Stan Bush has ever laid to tape.

BLOODSPORT SOUNDTRACK
1) &quot;On My Own - Alone&quot;
2) &quot;Fight to Survive&quot;

The widely circulated versions of this movies&amp;#039; soundtrack contain new versions of these songs performed by another unknown artist.  Many mp3s are making the rounds on P2P networks being attributed to Stan Bush even though the vocals are obviously not his.  These are the correct versions, which is also confirmed by the track lengths.

KICKBOXER SOUNDTRACK
1) &quot;Streets of Siam&quot;
2) &quot;Fight for Love&quot;
3) &quot;Never Surrender&quot;

While the Bloodsport soundtrack is available, it fetches respectable prices.  The Kickboxer soundtrack on the other hand is nearly impossible to find a copy of.  Because of that, I was unable to get the soundtrack version of &quot;Never Surrender&quot;.  Included here is the version from Stan&amp;#039;s solo album &quot;Call to Action&quot;.  The differences are very small and almost negligible.

TRANSFORMERS SOUNDTRACK
1) &quot;You&amp;#039;ve Got the Touch&quot;
2) &quot;Dare&quot;

Certainly the songs for which Stan is most famous, these are also two of his most powerful and positive songs.

BONUS REMIXES
1) &quot;You&amp;#039;ve Got the Touch&quot;
2) &quot;Dare&quot; 

From Stan&amp;#039;s album &quot;Call to Action&quot;, these updated versions of Stan&amp;#039;s previous hits are a must have for the hardcore fan.

ENJOY -- COMMENT -- SEED!
